## Objective
- Resume and continue a loopspace run for the gridcalc project, progressing through phases of building an in-memory spreadsheet engine with formula evaluation.

## Important Details
- Project: `/Users/arden/code/gridcalc-rerun` — Python 3.10+ pure-logic library, pytest test framework
