- Branch: `loopspace/gridcalc/phase-3` (checked out from phase-2 branch)
- Harness: opencode, tier C (role-swap protocol — orchestrator performs dispatches)
- Phase 1 complete: Sheet class with address validation, literal storage, eval_count property (tasks 1.1, 1.2)
- Phase 2 complete: Parser + evaluator with arithmetic, references, comparisons, error propagation (tasks 2.1, 2.2, 2.3)
- Phase 3 tasks: 3.1 (function grammar + SUM/MIN/MAX/COUNT), 3.2 (circular-reference detection)
- R12 sizing constraints: 512-char formulas, 32-deep parens, 256-cell chains must not raise RecursionError
- Error strings: `#PARSE!`, `#REF!`, `#TYPE!`, `#DIV!`, `#CYCLE!` (R5)
- Visit order for ranges: row-major; first error in visit order wins at value level

